    "402005": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Navia",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "This place has also been contaminated by Primordial Seawater."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Navia",
                    "T": "Yeah, and a lot of it, too. A Fontainian would most likely dissolve the moment they fell in."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "You should go back to safety, Navia."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Right, you can't go down if there's Primordial Seawater. It's too dangerous, and it won't be any help for you to just stay here."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Uh, don't get Paimon wrong... We're not saying you're useless! It's just that..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Navia",
                    "T": "No, you're right. I can't do anything in this situation. I'll leave this to you."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "We'll handle it! Just head back and be careful on the way out."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "From the look of things here..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Maybe there's no way back."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Navia",
                    "T": "That complicates things... Maybe the only way left is forward."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "In that case, do you want to wait for us here?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Navia",
                    "T": "The water levels here are unstable and there's a chance the water will rise... so staying here wouldn't be safe either."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Navia",
                    "T": "I'll go together with you — perhaps we'll find the exit just up ahead."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Seems like there isn't any other option."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Alright, come with us for now, then. But please, be careful!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
