    "402420": {
        "Desc": "Turn off all the spotlights",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": "Scene 5, Opera House, Furina"
                },
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": "Scene 6, Opera House, Furina"
                },
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": "Scene 182375, Opera House, Furina"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Unknown Voice",
                    "T": "Lady Furina! It's... It's like a dream, being able to speak with you up close like this..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Unknown Voice",
                    "T": "I've heard that the first member of our family who was honored to receive an audience with you was Madame Deoteria, almost twenty generations ago!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Furina",
                    "T": "Hahaha... And what a fine family yours is, indeed! It brings me great joy to meet such a faithful believer, a descendant of a line most ardent."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Unknown Voice",
                    "T": "Ehehe... Surely you exaggerate, Lady Furina..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Unknown Voice",
                    "T": "Um... My Lady?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Furina",
                    "T": "Hmm? What is it, good citizen..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Unknown Voice",
                    "T": "Are... are you crying?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Furina",
                    "T": "Eh... Huh? Hahaha, really now? I didn't even notice."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Furina",
                    "T": "*sigh* This must be the overflow of Hydro from my person! Well, can't quite help being the god whose dominion is the waters, can I?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Unknown Voice",
                    "T": "Ah, no wonder, no wonder... A manifestation of your power, then... O, Archon, I am honored to have witnessed it. Honored indeed..."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "402419": {
        "Desc": "Turn off all the spotlights",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Furina",
                    "T": "(The day's finally over. I haven't had a moment to breathe this whole time...)"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Furina",
                    "T": "(But it's good to see that everything's getting \"on track.\" There are no longer any voices of suspicion.)"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Furina",
                    "T": "(Maybe this is fine. I just need to keep going, and everyone will be saved...)"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Furina",
                    "T": "(Phew... Alright, Furina, don't think too hard about this. You need rest — tomorrow's a new day.)"
                },
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": "Scene 4, Opera House, Furina"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Unknown Voice",
                    "T": "Lady Furina, here are the new trial reports for the latest cases, as well as a summary of the follow-up..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Furina",
                    "T": "Ugh, there'll be no need for that. I've seen them already. There's no need to go back over scenes I've witnessed in person before!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": ""
                },
                {
                    "N": "Unknown Voice",
                    "T": "Lady Furina! I've waited for so, so long, for this chance to see you in this manner..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Furina",
                    "T": "Indeed, my dear, loyal citizen, this joyous moment is an honor for us both!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": ""
                },
                {
                    "N": "Unknown Voice",
                    "T": "Lady Furina. We're detecting significant hydrological anomalies near Poisson..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Furina",
                    "T": "Understood. Keep monitoring. Keep me informed should anything come up at the Institute."
                },
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": ""
                },
                {
                    "N": "Furina",
                    "T": "(Phew... I don't think I let anything slip today. I must show the people that there is nothing to worry about...)"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Furina",
                    "T": "(I just... don't know when these days will end...)"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Furina",
                    "T": "(I feel utterly exhausted. Best to rest early today, too.)"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
